ldap2dns (0.4.2-1~wgd1) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * New upstream release (0.4.2).
  * Non-maintainer upload (seems orphaned).
  * debian/compat: bump debhelper version to 7
  * debian/copyright: expanded and updated
  * debian/rules: set path variables used in Makefile
  * debian/rules: added get-orig-source target
  * debian/watch: support uscan against upstream github
  * debian/source/format: change to quilt patch system
  * debian/patches/ldap2dns-debian-config-path
  * debian/patches/makefile-bin-links: use symbolic links
  * debian/patches/makefile-let-debhelper-install-manpages
  * debian/patches/lintian-manpage-case-error: macro .b > .B
  * debian/manpages: man pages listed here instead of rules
  * debian/docs: added new plain text README from upstream
  * debian/rules: forget using links to genereate plain text README
  * debian/control: drop build-dep on links
  * debian/control: replace build-dep djbdns-installer with dbndns
  * debian/control: increased Standards-Version to 3.9.1
  * debian/ldap2dns.1: deprecated in favour of new upstream man page

